==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Referable
<hw>Ref"er*a*ble</hw> <pr>(r?f"?r*?*b'l)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Capable of being referred, or considered in relation to something
else; assignable; ascribable.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>referrible</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It is a question among philosophers, whether all the attractions
which obtain between bodies are <qex>referable</qex> to one general
cause.</q> <rj><qau>W. Nicholson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Referee</ent>⟦br⟧
